#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_analog.rst:2
msgid "Analog Evolution"
msgstr "Evolució Analògica"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_analog.rst:4
msgid ""
"The :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution` "
"functional simulates analog evolution of a quantum system under one or "
"more Hamiltonians, following a specified time-dependent schedule. Its "
"parameter interface mirrors that of "
":class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`, making it straightforward to "
"sweep control waveforms or pulse amplitudes from classical optimizers."
msgstr ""
"El funcional :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution` "
"simula l'evolució analògica d'un sistema quàntic sota un o més "
"Hamiltonians, seguint un programa dependent del temps especificat. La "
"seva interfície de paràmetres reflecteix la de "
":class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`, cosa que facilita el "
"recorregut de formes d'ona de control o amplituds de pols des "
"d'optimitzadors clàssics."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_analog.rst:8
msgid ""
"Observables and shot counts are specified separately via readout objects "
"passed to :meth:`~qilisdk.backends.backend.Backend.execute`."
msgstr ""
"Els observables i els comptatges de mesures s'especifiquen per separat "
"mitjançant objectes de lectura passats a "
":meth:`~qilisdk.backends.backend.Backend.execute`."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_analog.rst:11
msgid "**Parameters**"
msgstr "**Paràmetres**"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_analog.rst:13
msgid ""
"**schedule** (:class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`): Defines total "
"evolution time, time steps, Hamiltonians, and their time-dependent "
"coefficients."
msgstr ""
"**schedule** (:class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`): Defineix el "
"temps total d'evolució, els passos de temps, els Hamiltonians i els seus "
"coeficients dependents del temps."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_analog.rst:14
msgid ""
"**initial_state** (:class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor`): Initial state"
" of the system."
msgstr ""
"**initial_state** (:class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor`): Estat inicial"
" del sistema."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_analog.rst:15
msgid ""
"**store_intermediate_results** (bool, optional): If True, records the "
"state at each time step. Default is False."
msgstr ""
"**store_intermediate_results** (bool, opcional): Si és True, registra "
"l'estat en cada pas de temps. El valor per defecte és False."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_analog.rst:17
msgid "**Returns**"
msgstr "**Retorna**"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals_analog.rst:19
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`: Inspect"
" "
":meth:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.get_expectation_values`"
" for measured observables, "
":meth:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.get_state`"
" for the closing state, and "
":meth:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.get_intermediate_states`"
" and "
":meth:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.get_intermediate_expectation_values`"
" when ``store_intermediate_results`` is enabled."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`: "
"Consulteu "
":meth:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.get_expectation_values`"
" per als observables mesurats, "
":meth:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.get_state`"
" per a l'estat final, i "
":meth:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.get_intermediate_states`"
" i "
":meth:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult.get_intermediate_expectation_values`"
" quan ``store_intermediate_results`` està activat."

